==評價==
本片收获了极大的好评，[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]新鲜度达82%，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分73。影评人[[Roger_Ebert|Roger Ebert]]给出满分的四颗星。

[[美國電影學會|美國電影學會]]和[[国家评论协会|国家评论协会]]都将其列為2007年十大佳片之一<ref>{{cite web | last =  | first =  | authorlink =  | coauthors =  | title = No Country for Old Men, Juno named to AFI's Top 10 of year | work =  | publisher = [[CBC_News|CBC]] | date = 2007-12-17 | url = http://www.cbc.ca/arts/film/story/2007/12/17/afi-top-films.html?ref=rss | format =  | doi =  | accessdate = 2007-12-31 | archive-date = 2008-01-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080108160557/http://www.cbc.ca/arts/film/story/2007/12/17/afi-top-films.html?ref=rss | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.afi.com/tvevents/afiawards07/default.aspx AFI AWARDS 2007] {{Wayback|url=http://www.afi.com/tvevents/afiawards07/default.aspx |date=20110605081545 }}, [[American_Film_Institute|American Film Institute]]</ref>。2008年《[[帝国杂志|帝国杂志]]》在评选500大佳片时，本片位列第473名<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.empireonline.com/500/5.asp |title=empireonline |accessdate=2013-08-04 |archive-date=2011-08-28 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/61GcY3Qpx?url=http://www.empireonline.com/500/5.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==後續效應==
影片中男主角所待的廢棄巴士「費班克142號巴士」（{{lang|en|Fairbanks Bus 142}}）隨著電影播出而爆紅，有些影迷特地遠赴阿拉斯加[[朝聖_(通俗)|朝聖]]該輛巴士，但因巴士所在地相當偏遠，離最近的城鎮約50公里，並非完善規劃的旅遊景點，且需跨過湍急的[[提克蘭尼卡河|提克蘭尼卡河]]（Teklanika River），歷年來已造成15起搜救事件，有2人被河水沖走<ref>{{cite news |url=https://money.udn.com/money/story/10511/4648482 |title=「阿拉斯加之死」朝聖意外多 廢棄巴士被遷離 |author=中央通訊社 |publisher=經濟日報 |date=2020-06-19 |accessdate=2020-06-21 |archive-date=2020-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200621143445/https://money.udn.com/money/story/10511/4648482 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。阿拉斯加當地政府有鑑於每次搜救需耗費龐大資源與[[社會成本|社會成本]]，為防止遊客繼續前往，在和自然資源部協調後，2020年6月18日由[[美國陸軍國民警衛隊|陸軍國民警衛隊]]派出一架[[CH-47|CH-47]]契努克（Chinook）直升機將該巴士吊離現場<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/50809#ixzz6PytgKZaz |title=《阿拉斯加之死》廢棄公車吸引更多死亡　「軍機載它上天」尋覓安全地 |publisher=ETtoday新聞雲 |date=2020-06-20 |accessdate=2020-06-21 |archive-date=2020-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200622090953/https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/50809#ixzz6PytgKZaz |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年7月30日，阿拉斯加州自然資源部宣佈將此輛巴士安置在費班克的[[阿拉斯加大學|阿拉斯加大學]]北方博物館（Museum of the North）保存展示<ref>{{cite press |url=http://www.dnr.alaska.gov/mlw/news/bus-142/pdf/7-30-20-DNR-to-pursue-safeguarding-Stampede-Trail-Bus-at-UA-Museum.pdf |title=DNR to pursue safeguarding Stampede Trail bus at UA Museum |publisher=Department of Natural Resources |date=2020-07-30 |language=en |access-date=2020-08-01 |archive-date=2020-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731200035/http://www.dnr.alaska.gov/mlw/news/bus-142/pdf/7-30-20-DNR-to-pursue-safeguarding-Stampede-Trail-Bus-at-UA-Museum.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

